1 0 0 1 50 578 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 564 Tm (query_tokens x key_tokens) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 550 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 536 Tm (For image generation, query_tokens can be large because many latent image positions are ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 522 Tm (asking questions at once. At 1024x1024, the latent has far more spatial work than at ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 508 Tm (512x512. Attention can become a major peak-memory cost.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 494 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 480 Tm (What Attention Slicing Tries To Do) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 466 Tm () Tj
