1 0 0 1 50 508 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 494 Tm (This is grouped-query attention, also called GQA. It is a legitimate efficiency design. ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 480 Tm (Several query heads share fewer key/value heads.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 466 Tm () Tj
