1 0 0 1 50 522 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 508 Tm (Then the outputs are concatenated and projected:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 494 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 480 Tm (combined = concat\(head_outputs\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 466 Tm (output = Wout combined + bout) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 452 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 438 Tm (This combined result feeds the next UNet layer.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 424 Tm () Tj
